<h2> <span class="mw-headline" id="This_Week.27s_Focus">This Week's Focus</span></h2>
<ul>
<li>This weeks focus will be on Common and Public goods, as the last 7 weeks have focused primarily on private goods.  </li>
<li>We will also touch on club goods like cable TV and internet content.</li>
</ul>

